Feline2::
She blushed as he kissed her cheek.  She looked deep into his eyes 
and thought she saw something. She wondered it he  really felt that 
way. She was beginning to wonder if bots from other factions could 
find love.  She smiled at him and kissed him. She felt electricity 
and fire in his kiss.
